{"tid":826592,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"開錯個頭可以點做","createTime":"2018-09-18T10:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T14:57:45.000Z","uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3ddcb3dcb8bd7abe5738143d280c8263a33012","tid":826592,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"grad 之後一張白紙難搵工<br />\n求其入左間好奀既細公司，做php<br />\nunderpaid 但都見學到野，老細都教我唔少野<br />\n後來跳黎跳去都係細公司，做黎做去都係php,細project,同埋同之前重復既野<br />\n呢兩年經驗實際同人一年經驗差唔多<br />\n有兩份工只係做左3個月，最耐都只係9個月<br />\nd 公司好多見我cv 花就唔想請<br />\n<br />\n之前搵工，除左第一份之外，都唔係學到好多野<br />\n有兩份都係返工先發現用既tech／practice仲落後過上份，<br />\n不過其中一份就都有少少新proj 但都係細proj，工時長，做半年同阿頭唔夾之後被辭職<br />\n一份真係學到野，一個人一腳踢做哂所有野，不過老細超仆街，連mpf都扣鳩人，一個月就走<br />\n<br />\n點樣先可以返正途<br />\n或者唔想繼續做php可以點？<br />\n而家學緊nodejs同react 要做到咩成果先夠出黎搵食？"},{"pid":"ffeff998f5404f0ccdfc46cdfe632be6068a75e7","tid":826592,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79140cb415f3edbd22166f055cae134821b21a3b","tid":826592,"uid":34217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:48:14.000Z","msg":"咩叫正途?"},{"pid":"cb38cbc7bdf9d6563e7993a2c838e719f79785e6","tid":826592,"uid":23953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:05:46.000Z","msg":"樓主應該學下interview 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db3873f5ce78732bf66f0acf1ed673104f214c2","tid":826592,"uid":41134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:35:22.000Z","msg":"自己寫下野放上GitHub"},{"pid":"a35093616945cf4f6dfbe308185fea7c08138a04","tid":826592,"uid":75139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cb38cbc7bdf9d6563e7993a2c838e719f79785e6","tid":826592,"uid":23953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:05:46.000Z","msg":"樓主應該學下interview 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm